pullrequest.title: Remove underscores from robot model names in fuel URI

content.raw: DARPA wants to keep the same title format for the `Xn Config n` names in Fuel. For the teams submissions; which includes the Explorer, @{557058:10b01d41-a2e9-4a41-a907-e6e2f03b6cd5} is updating the script to default to whatever exact name they used. For both, download URI and launch it.
